insertion_sort([], []).
insertion_sort([H|T], Sorted) :-
    insertion_sort(T, SortedTail),
    insert(H, SortedTail, Sorted).
insert(X, [], [X]).
insert(X, [H|T], [X,H|T]) :-
    X =< H.
insert(X, [H|T], [H|Inserted]) :-
    X > H,
    insert(X, T, Inserted).
